social_posts.post_text: Odds stacked against me, I only go harder … 💫
Never been a people person, always been the people’s person 🦋🖤#grateful
Walk by faith, not by sight
Like the cultivation of a flower … one day at a time …🌹

Very happy to begin my professional career here in Costa Rica. Thank you to God, my family, my supporters, and all those involved. New team, new country, new challenges but with the same faith and motivation as always.

Muy feliz de comenzar mi carrera profesional aquí en Costa Rica. Gracias a Dios, a mi familia, a mis seguidores y a todos los involucrados. Nuevo equipo, nuevo país, nuevos retos pero con la misma fe y motivación de siempre. 

AP9 💙🖤🤍
Cada día más cerca al objetivo 💪

Fue una noche con muchas emociones diferentes. Pero ahí empezó la primera página de un nuevo capitulo. Siempre agradecido con Dios que me permite jugar este deporte tan hermoso. 

It was a night filled with many different emotions. But there began the first page of this new chapter. Always grateful to God who allows me to play this beautiful sport. 

Vamos por mas 🤍💙🖤

text_entities.entity: always grateful to god who allows me to play this beautiful sport

social_posts.post_text:
Dear Soccer,

As I reflect on our journey together, I am overwhelmed with gratitude & emotion. It all started with a dream — a dream that set the stage for a remarkable journey. 

You have been more than just a sport to me — rather a companion through highs & lows, a constant form of expression, and the canvas on which I painted my dreams. 

I not only found a game, but a world of opportunities. You opened doors I never knew existed and paved the way for incredible experiences. Moments that are etched in my heart forever. 

You have gifted me friendships that transcend beyond the boundaries of a game. I am grateful to have met so many amazing people from different walks of life and parts of the world. 

You, soccer, have been the catalyst for dreams coming true — I am forever in debt to this beautiful game.

With love,
AP9
